metadata.description:
NFTSCAN is a professional NFT assets browser and data analysis platform.Dedicated to building the infrastructure of the blockchain world and providing high-quality blockchain data support and services for developers and users.
NFTSCAN project development progress:
 
   1) The NFTSCAN project was launched in early April 2021;
 
   2) NFTSCAN released the public beta on July 22, 2021（https://nftscan.net/）;
 
   3) NFTSCAN released the official version on September 3, 2021（https://nftscan.com/）;

Business introduction:
 1、Institution-end business:
 
	1) NFTSCAN will launch an open API platform for NFT data to provide data services for NFT developers;
 
      2) Provide data consulting services for organizations and institutions;
 
   2、Client-end business:
 
      1) Develop and maintain existing NFTSCAN browser to provide users with NFT asset data search and query services
 
	2) Provide account and public homepage features for NFT project parties、 artists and collectors for signature authentication and basic information display of NFT-related addresses.
 
      3) Paid services for NFT professional investors, such as NFT giant whale address tracking、NFT trading lists、NFT minting lists and other related data hot lists.
 
   3、Innovative business: provide NFT transaction related functions on the asset details page of the NFTSCAN browser.

Data status:

1) Number of NFT assets: 27.35 million pieces;
2) Number of NFT asset contracts: 24,838;
3) NFT-related transaction records: 42.15 million;
4) NFT related wallet addresses: 3.35 million;

NFTSCAN's development plan for the half year:
 
   2021.09.30：Launch the NFTSCAN API open platform to provide developers with NFT API services.
 
   2021.10.31：Launch of NFTSCAN version 2.0, with new features such as account system, public homepage, and signature authentication.
 
   2021.11.30: Support NFT data of multiple blockchain networks.
 
   2022.03.01: Release NFTSCAN mobile APP, namely NFTSCAN APP.
